# Wumpus World CNF (local area around (1,1), (1,2), (2,1), (2,2))
# Propositions:
#   Pxy   = there is a pit in cell (x,y)
#   Bxy   = there is a breeze in cell (x,y)
#   safe22 = cell (2,2) is safe (no pit in 2,2)
#
# World layout 
# (1,3) (2,3) (3,3)
# (1,2) (2,2) (3,2)
# (1,1) (2,1) (3,1)


# start square has no pit
-P11

# There is a pit in at least one of the squares next to it.
# If there is a pit next to a square, that square will have a breeze

# B11 <-> (P12 or P21)
# B11 -> (P12 or P21)
-B11 P12 P21
# (P12 -> B11) and (P21 -> B11)
-P12 B11
-P21 B11

# B12 <-> (P11 or P13 or P22)
# B12 -> (P11 or P13 or P22)
-B12 P11 P13 P22
# (P11 -> B12), (P13 -> B12), (P22 -> B12)
-P11 B12
-P13 B12
-P22 B12

# B21 <-> (P11 or P22 or P31)
# B21 -> (P11 or P22 or P31)
-B21 P11 P22 P31
# (P11 -> B21), (P22 -> B21), (P31 -> B21)
-P11 B21
-P22 B21
-P31 B21

-safe22 -P22
P22 safe22